            <tr>
              <td class="events">
                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="ADVENT"></a>ADVENTure in Sanderstead 1 - 24 December</h3>
                <p>ADVENTure is back in Sanderstead this Christmas. From 1st till 24th December a different location each evening will open for one hour between 6pm and 7pm. The theme this year is "There is room for all in the ADVENTure Ark". How many animals will you spot? Refreshments, Music, Lights. Full details of all the locations are available on <%= link_to "sanderstead-parish.org.uk", "https://www.sanderstead-parish.org.uk/pages/adventure2018" %>.</p>
              </td>
              <td class="events"><%= link_to image_tag("small-images/all_saints100.jpg", alt: "All Saints logo"), "http://www.sanderstead-parish.org.uk/all_saints" %>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="events">
                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="URC"></a>Christmas Services during December at Sanderstead URC</h3>
                <p>Services during Advent and Christmas at the URC including Candlelight Carol Service on Sunday 16th December at 6.30 pm and Christingle and Crib Service on Christmas Eve at 4 pm. <%= link_to "View all the services on this flyer", "resource/URC_Christmas.pdf" %></p>
              </td>
              <td class="events"><%= link_to image_tag("small-images/surc.jpg", alt: "SURC logo"), "http://www.surc.org.uk" %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="events">
                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="soul"></a>Soul Symphony Concert Saturday 8th December at 6.30 pm</h3>
                <p>Why not come to Soul Symphony Choir’s concert on Saturday 8th December at Selsdon Baptist Church from 6:30pm, raising funds for We-STAP who supply toiletries and sanitary products to women in need in Croydon? Tickets available at the door or for a reduced rate using <%= link_to "www.ticketsource.co.uk/soul-symphony-choir-winter", "http://www.ticketsource.co.uk/soul-symphony-choir-winter" %></p>
                <p>Soul Symphony is a community choir that meets on Tuesday evenings from 7:15pm at The Holy Family RC Church hall in Limpsfield Road, near to Waitrose. All are very welcome; no previous singing experience is required. If you are interested in joining please visit <%= link_to "www.soulsymphony.co.uk", "http://www.soulsymphony.co.uk" %> for more information.</p>
               </td>
              <td class="events"><%= link_to image_tag("small-images/Soul symphony100.jpg", alt: "Soul Symphony"), "resource/Soul_Symphony_2018.pdf" %>

              </td>

             <tr>
