                <p><%= link_to "Christmas Craft for Adults and Children!", "resource/xmas_craft.pdf" %> Tuesday 11th December from 3.30-4.30pm. Have fun with our Christmas craft session for adults and children! The Sanderstead WI are kindly running the adult craft Please book for the adult Christmas craft.</p>
                <p>Sanderstead Library, Farm Fields, South Croydon, CR2 0HL. Telephone: 020 3700 1015 Email: sandersteadlibrary@croydon.gov.uk</p>
              </td>
